{"type": "article", "id": 10192, "title": "女足国家队加入 FIFA 游戏豪华战队", "description": "提示：您的当家球星因为怀孕将缺席九个月。", "date": "2015-06-01T09:31:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13, "name": "游戏"}, {"id": 755, "name": "足球"}, {"id": 1072, "name": "FIFA"}, {"id": 7508, "name": "EA"}, {"id": 10858, "name": "KONAMI"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604230524ULiuROFNPyC3JdtX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style>@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"Times\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"宋体\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"Cambria Math\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"@宋体\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"Cambria\";\r\n}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal { margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; }p { margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Times; }.MsoChpDefault { font-family: Cambria; }div.WordSection1 { page: WordSection1; }</style>\r\n</head>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">每当球队输球的时候，球迷们就会默默打开 FIFA……在游戏里胖揍一顿对手。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">现在女子足球队也加入 FIFA 豪华战线啦！美国艺电<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (Electronic Arts，</span>简称<span lang=\"EN-US\"> EA )</span>宣布《<span lang=\"EN-US\">FIFA 16</span>》将于今年 <span lang=\"EN-US\">9 </span>月 <span lang=\"EN-US\">22 </span>日发售，并且首次引入 <span lang=\"EN-US\">12 </span>支“女足国家队”：中国、澳大利亚、巴西、加拿大、英国、法国、德国、意大利、墨西哥、西班牙、瑞典以及美国。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135522A8FRoybIafjDvJ39.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41919192\" data-format=\"gif\"></span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\" lang=\"EN-US\">FIFA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\"> 系列是世界上最流行的足球类电子游戏之一，\r\n自 <span lang=\"EN-US\">93 </span>年发行以来，<span lang=\"EN-US\">EA </span>每年都会更新版本，另外还会发行世界杯及欧锦赛特别版，在全球已经累计了几亿玩家。去年 <span lang=\"EN-US\">FIFAOL3</span> 官方宣布其同时在线人数已经突破<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 50 </span>万，刷新了体育类网游的在线记录。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">本次更新的女足模式拥有快速比赛，线下锦标赛和线上友谊赛三种玩法可供选择，为了让<span lang=\"EN-US\"> FIFA </span>女足的亮相足够惊艳，<span lang=\"EN-US\">EA </span>在处理球员动态捕捉、<span lang=\"EN-US\">360</span> 度人体扫描上费尽心思，并邀请了顶级女子足球运动员 <span lang=\"EN-US\">Abby Wambach </span>在内的多位女国脚拍摄<span lang=\"EN-US\"> FIFA </span>16 女足宣传片。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=h0155eqi1qc&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"498\" width=\"640\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\" lang=\"EN-US\">FIFA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\"> 系列制作人 <span lang=\"EN-US\">David Rutter</span> 表示，能够获得世界上最优秀的女足球员和球队特许经营权算得上是 <span lang=\"EN-US\">EA </span>的大事件。而 <span lang=\"EN-US\">2011 </span>年世界杯冠军日本女足的“缺位”也再次将<span lang=\"EN-US\"> FIFA </span>和老对手《实况足球》的较劲摆到了台面上。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">作为最早的足球类电子游戏，《实况足球》由日本游戏软件<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/3094449.htm\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\"></span></a></span>巨头<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/47092.htm\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none;\"> KONAMI </span></a></span>出品。外界普遍猜测，和以往 <span lang=\"EN-US\">FIFA </span>游戏里日本国家队和日本联赛的“集体失踪”一样，<span lang=\"EN-US\">EA </span>这次也没能拿到日本女子国家队的特许经营权。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230521Led1Upry4JHxfYcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">作为足球电子游戏领域的后来者，<span lang=\"EN-US\">EA </span>与竞争对手《实况足球》缠斗多年。后者凭借精美的日系画工和强大的还原真实效果，曾经独霸足球游戏世界。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230522bJV7YALwv2XrPzp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">而<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2009 </span>年，<span lang=\"EN-US\">EA </span>一举拿下了国际足联对于 <span lang=\"EN-US\">33 </span>个联赛、<span lang=\"EN-US\">12,850</span> 名真实的球星、<span lang=\"EN-US\">44</span> 个体育场馆以及俱乐部球衣等真实道具的官方授权，推出了世界上首款以真实世界足球赛事和球员为模型的在线游戏《<span lang=\"EN-US\">FIFA Online 2</span>》，终于打破了 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/47092.htm\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none;\">KONAMI</span></a></span> 《实况足球》的垄断地位，在制作水平上也不断提升。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230522rV2O9hIUy7pWujC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\">FIFA 系列与《实况足球》历年销量对比（<span style=\"color:#222222;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.1000003814697px;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:1;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;\">单位：M</span>）：<br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230523WupkNeSLK6maZQjb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t（PES6 被认为是实况的扛鼎之作，数据证明也成为了销量拐点）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:11.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:17.25pt;background:white;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\"mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;'>作为目前中国第一的体育类游戏，<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> <span>EA </span></span>也将中国视为 FIFA 系列的重要战略市场。上个月，<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> <span>EA\r\nSports</span> </span> 举办“崛起，中国足球”公测发布会，宣布<span lang=\"EN-US\"> FIFA </span>系列将首次加入包括恒大、国安、鲁能、人和在内的多支中超球队，范志毅、郝海东等知名中国球星将以传奇球员的身份植入游戏。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:11.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:17.25pt;background:white;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230523AKkRs0Jih2MyvZ4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\"mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;'><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:11.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:17.25pt;background:white;\" align=\"justify\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" align=\"justify\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"display:none;\" id=\"__if72ru4sdfsdfrkjahiuyi_once\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"__zsc_once\" align=\"justify\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"display:none;\" id=\"__hggasdgjhsagd_once\">\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}